# ⚙️ COA Concept 4: AI Training Bottlenecks

---

## 1️⃣ AI Training Needs

✔ huge computation
✔ massive memory
✔ large datasets

---

## Common Bottlenecks

---

## 🔹 Memory Bandwidth

GPU waiting for data.

---

## 🔹 Communication Overhead

Multiple GPUs exchanging parameters.

---

## 🔹 Storage Throughput

Data loading too slow.

---

## 🔹 Synchronization Cost

Devices waiting for each other.

---

## 🧠 Real-World Analogy

Fast workers slowed by slow material delivery.

---

## 🎯 Placement Question

